  1. La chn tnh nng:

Bi tp ny tp trung vo phn tch tc b nh ca GPU. Tc xung nhp b nh c tc ng ng k n hiu sut ca GPU, c bit trong cc tc v i hi truy cp d liu ln. Xung nhp b nh cao hn cho php GPU truy cp b nh nhanh hn, t nng cao hiu sut tng th. Mt s tnh nng quan trng c la chn nh gi tc b nh,bao gm: Memory_Bandwidth,Memory ,Memory_Speed, L2_Cache, Memory_Bus, Dedicated,Shader, Manufacturer.

  1. Kim tra d liu khuyt trong tp tin.

Tm cc hng trng (tc l cc hng m ton b gi tr l rng hoc ) trong d liu v chuyn i chng thnh gi tr NA.

# Thay th tt c cc  trng trong d liu GPU_data bng NA
All_GPUs[All_GPUs == ""] <- NA

Tm cc gi tr trong dataframe c nh dng l du gch ngang (cc gi tr bt u bng k t xung dng v theo sau l du -) v thay th chng bng gi tr NA. S dng lnh gsub() thay th tt c cc du - trong dataframe thnh NA m bo vic x l d liu c nht qun.

# Thay th cc gi tr c nh dng "\n-" bng NA trong tt c cc ct ca GPU_data
All_GPUs[] <- lapply(All_GPUs, function(x) gsub("^\\n- $", NA, x))

# Thay th cc chui "NA" bng NA
All_GPUs[All_GPUs == "NA"] <- NA

Nu hm gsub() khng th trc tip chuyn cc gi tr thnh NA v NA khng phi l mt chui k t, th c th thay th cc gi tr ny thnh chui "NA" trc. Sau , nu cn, chuyn i cc chui "NA" trong dataframe thnh gi tr NA thc s m bo d liu c chun ha ng cch. Kt qu c hin th trong hnh 2.

D liu khuyt trong bng cho thy mt s bin c t l khuyt rt cao, c bit l Release_Price (84%), DisplayPort_Connection (75%), v Boost_Clock (58%). Nhng bin ny cn x l c bit nu ng vai tr quan trng trong phn tch. Cc bin nh PSU (34%), Core_Speed (27%), v cc kt ni (HDMI, VGA, DVI) thiu t 20-35%, nh hng n kh nng phn tch tnh nng k thut. Mt s bin c t l khuyt di 20% (Best_Resolution, Max_Power, Pixel_Rate, Texture_Rate) v di 10% (Memory, Shader) c th d dng c in d liu. c bit, mt s bin quan trng nh L2_Cache, Manufacturer, Name v Release_Date khng b khuyt, gip m bo tin cy cho cc phn tch chnh yu. X l hiu qu d liu khuyt s ci thin cht lng ca cc kt lun t b d liu ny.

Da trn kt qu thu c, c th nhn thy rng kh nhiu bin cha d liu khuyt. V vy, trc quan ha t l ny, ta cn s dng hm t th vin ggplot2 v biu th hin t l d liu khuyt cho tng bin. Vic ny gip d dng nhn din v nh gi mc khuyt ca d liu trong tng ct, h tr cc quyt nh x l d liu hiu qu hn.

# Lc cc ct c t l d liu khuyt di 15%

Quy trnh lm sch d liu s gi li cc gi tr NA tr khi vic loi b chng l thc s cn thit. Trong mt s trng hp, cc gi tr NA c th cha thng tin quan trng m khng nn xa b ty tin; v vy, chng khng lun c xem l d liu khng hp l. Da vo bi cnh nghin cu, khi chng ta tp trung vo cc mu d liu c th, chin lc x l gi tr NA s c iu chnh linh hot m bo khng b st bt k thng tin no c gi tr.

Nh ta thy, do t l NA trong cc bin ny l kh thp, v b d liu All_GPUs tng i ln nn vic loi b cc hng cha gi tr NA s khng gy tc ng ln n tnh i din ca d liu. Ngay c khi loi b mt s lng ng k cc quan st, tp d liu cn li vn ln cung cp kt qu ng tin cy v h tr cho cc phn tch chuyn su. Kt

  1. Lm sch cc bin v x l nh dng cc bin:

Nhn thy rng tt c d liu trong mt tnh nng u s dng cng mt n v o. thun li hn cho vic quan st v phn tch, chng ti quyt nh loi b tt c cc n v khi cc tnh nng nh L2_Cache,Memory_Bandwidth,Memory_Bus,Memory_Speed,Memory v Process. Vic ny khng ch gip tng tnh ng nht trong phn tch m cn n gin ha vic so snh v din gii d liu trn cc tnh nng ny.

# La chn cc bin cn xo n v
  columns_to_clean <- c("L2_Cache","Memory_Bandwidth","Memory_Bus","Memory_Speed", "Memory", "Process" )

#To hm thc hin xo n v  cc bin 
  remove_units <- function(column) {
# S dng gsub  xa tt c cc k t khng phi s (k c n v)
  cleaned_column <- gsub("[^0-9.]", "", column)
# Chuyn i kt qu v kiu numeric
  cleaned_column <- as.numeric(cleaned_column)
  
  return(cleaned_column)
  }
  
# p dng hm cho cc bin  chn
new_GPU_data[columns_to_clean] <- lapply(new_GPU_data[columns_to_clean], remove_units)

Sau khi tin hnh lm sch b d liu, chng ta thu c 19 bin cng vi 2637 quan st c gi tr. Giai on tip theo ca l xc nh v la chn cc bin quan trng, trong Memory_Bandwidth ni bt nh mt yu t thit yu trong vic nh gi hiu sut ca cc GPU.

phn tch cc yu t nh hng n Memory_Bandwidth, m hnh hi quy c la chn l phng php n gin nhng hiu qu. Trong m hnh ny, chng ta xem Memory_Bandwidth l bin ph thuc, trong khi cc bin c lp qua x l bao gm: Memory_Speed, L2_Cache, Architecture, Dedicated, Memory_Bus, Shader, Direct_X, v Resolution_WxH.

Tuy nhin, cc bin Architecture, Direct_X, v Resolution_WxH l nhng bin dng chui c nhiu gi tr khc nhau, lm tng phc tp cho m hnh hi quy. Do , ti u ha phn tch, chng ta s gi li cc bin c lp nh Memory, Memory_Speed, L2_Cache, Memory_Bus, Shader v Dedicated. Trc khi tin hnh phn tch d liu, cn phn bit r gia bin nh lng v bin phn loi. Bin nh lng l nhng bin c gi tr s hc, cho php thc hin cc php ton v phn tch thng k, bao gm c bin lin tc (nh chiu cao, nhit ) v bin ri rc (nh s lng sn phm). Trong khi , bin phn loi dng biu th cc nhm hoc c im, chng hn nh gii tnh, mu sc, hoc loi sn phm. Cc bin ny thng c biu din bng nhn v khng ph hp cho cc php tnh s hc. Vic phn loi chnh xc cc bin ny gip la chn phng php phn tch ph hp, t nng cao chnh xc v gi tr ca kt qu phn tch.

i vi cc bin nh lng, bao gm c bin lin tc v ri rc, chng ta tin hnh tnh cc thng k m t nh trung bnh, lch chun mu, cc phn v, trung v, gi tr ln nht v gi tr nh nht. Nhng thng k ny gip chng ta c ci nhn ton din hn v s phn b v c im ca d liu.

summary_stats <- sapply(numeric_data, function(x) {
  c(
    Mean = mean(x),                   # Trung bnh
    SD = sd(x),                       #  lch chun
    Min = min(x),                     # Gi tr nh nht
    Q1 = quantile(x, 0.25),           # Phn v 25%
    Median = median(x),               # Trung v
    Q3 = quantile(x, 0.75),           # Phn v 75%
    Max = max(x)                      # Gi tr ln nht
  )
})

Da vo th, c th thy r mt s c im ni bt trong phn phi ca Memory Bandwidth (Y). Trc ht, th ny cho thy phn phi lch tri r rt, vi phn ln d liu tp trung mc bng thng thp, t 0 n 200 GB/s. T nhng c im trn, c th khng nh rng Y khng tun theo phn phi chun. Mt phn phi chun thng thng c hnh dng i xng, vi phn ln d liu tp trung quanh gi tr trung bnh v gim u v hai pha. Trong trng hp ny, s tp trung d liu bng thng thp cng vi ui di v bn phi to nn lch ng k, iu ny c th nh hng n cc phn tch i hi tnh chun ca d liu, chng hn nh hi quy tuyn tnh thng thng.

  • Chun Ha Cho Bin Memory Bandwidth (Y) v cc bin nh hng n Y nh Memory_Speed,L2_Cache,Memory_Bus,Memory:

chun ha d liu trong trng hp ny, chng ta s p dng php bin i logarit cho bin Memory Bandwidth (Y) v cc bin Memory_Speed,L2_Cache,Memory_Bus,Memory . Vic ny nhm lm gim nh hng ca cc gi tr cc ln v gip phn phi tr nn gn vi phn phi chun hn, t ci thin hiu qu ca cc m hnh phn tch da trn gi nh tnh chun (nh hi quy tuyn tnh).

Php chun ha logarit cho bin c th c biu din nh sau:

     ln(Y) = b0 + b1*ln(X1) + b2*ln(X2) +  +

Trong :
- ln(): l gi tr chun ha ca Y bng php bin i logarit t nhin.
- 0,1,2,: l cc tham s hi quy cn c lng.
- 1,2,: l cc bin c lp (cc yu t nh hng n ).
- : l sai s ngu nhin trong m hnh.

# Chun ha Bin Memory_Bandwidth(Y) v cc bin nh hng n Y nh Memory_Speed,L2_Cache,Memory_Bus,Memory:
main_GPU_data$Memory_Bandwidth <- log(main_GPU_data$Memory_Bandwidth)
main_GPU_data$Memory_Speed <- log(main_GPU_data$Memory_Speed + 1 )
main_GPU_data$L2_Cache <- log(main_GPU_data$L2_Cache + 1 )
main_GPU_data$Memory_Bus <- log(main_GPU_data$Memory_Bus + 1 )
main_GPU_data$Memory <- log(main_GPU_data$Memory +1 )

xc nh liu Memory_Bandwidth c phn phi chun hay khng, ta thc hin kim nh vi cc gi thuyt sau:

  • Gi thuyt H1: Bin Memory_Bandwidth khng c phn phi chun.

  • Nu p-value < 5%: Bc b gi thuyt H0, cho thy d liu khng tun theo phn phi chun.

n <- length(main_GPU_data$Memory_Bandwidth)

  • t Gi Thuyt
  • Gi thuyt 0: Phng sai ca nhm 1 bng phng sai ca nhm 2, tc l 1^2 = 2^2.
  • Gi thuyt H1: Phng sai ca nhm 1 ln hn phng sai ca nhm 2, tc l 1^2 > 2^2

Lu : Du bt ng thc trong gi thuyt thay i ty thuc vo cc gi tr mu. Trong trng hp ny, v 1 >2 , chng ta s kim nh xem phng sai ca nhm 1 c ln hn phng sai ca nhm 2 hay khng.
